---
import Website from '../layouts/website.astro';
import { IconArrowDownRight, IconCircleSquare, IconCircleDashed, IconChartDonut2, IconBrandSupabase, IconServer, IconRefresh, IconBrandFirebase, IconDeviceTablet, IconPointer, IconPencil, IconEdit, IconWorld, IconDeviceDesktop, IconArrowRight, IconClockHour3 } from '@tabler/icons-preact';
---

<Website title="Marcus Felix - Developer">
	<main class="container mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="h-[30vh]"></div>
		<div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
			<div class="flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row gap-4">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-gray-100 border-2 border-gray-100 px-2 py-2 pr-6 rounded-full text-lg">
					<span class="flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7">
						<span class="bg-green-600 w-3 h-3 rounded-full animate-ping absolute"></span>
						<span class="bg-green-500 w-3 h-3 rounded-full absolute"></span>
					</span>
					Available to work
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-lg">
					<span class="flex items-center border-2 px-3 py-2 pr-4 gap-1 rounded-full">
						<span class="slow-spin"><IconCircleDashed size={24} /></span> 5 
					</span>
					Spots available
				</div>
			</div>
			<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl md:max-w-6xl text-black leading-[72px] md:leading-[82px]">Senior developer & designer crafting digital experiences for web and mobile</h1>
			<nav class="text-2xl">
				<span class="flex items-center gap-4"><IconArrowDownRight size={28}/> Latest work</span>
			</nav>
		</div>
	</main>
	<div class="h-10"></div>
	<section class="overflow-y-auto pb-4">
		<div class="flex gap-6 px-6">
			<a href="https://github.com/marcusfelix/caster" target="_blank" class="flex flex-col gap-2 w-full min-w-sm max-w-sm shrink-0">
				<img src="assets/caster-1.jpeg" class="object-fit rounded-2xl border-2 hover:border-black transition-all"/>
				<p class="px-4">Home screen - Caster</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/marcusfelix/hausmeister" target="_blank" class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full min-w-sm max-w-sm shrink-0">
				<img src="assets/hausmeister-1.jpeg" class="object-fit rounded-2xl border-2 hover:border-black transition-all"/>
				<p class="px-4">Home screen - Hausmeister</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/marcusfelix/caster" target="_blank" class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full min-w-sm max-w-sm shrink-0">
				<img src="assets/caster-2.jpeg" class="object-fit rounded-2xl border-2 hover:border-black transition-all"/>
				<p class="px-4">Podcast player - Caster</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/marcusfelix/hausmeister" target="_blank" class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full min-w-sm max-w-sm shrink-0">
				<img src="assets/hausmeister-4.jpeg" class="object-fit rounded-2xl border-2 hover:border-black transition-all"/>
				<p class="px-4">Ticket detail - Hausmeister</p>
			</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/marcusfelix/caster" target="_blank" class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full min-w-sm max-w-sm shrink-0">
				<img src="assets/caster-3.jpeg" class="object-fit rounded-2xl border-2 hover:border-black transition-all"/>
				<p class="px-4">Chat view - Caster</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
	<div class="h-32"></div>
	<section class="container mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
			<nav class="text-2xl w-full max-w-sm">
				<span class="flex items-center gap-4 text-black"><IconArrowDownRight size={28}/>Services</span>
			</nav>
			<div class="w-full grid grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-x-4 gap-y-6">
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconEdit/> Branding</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconCircleSquare/> Icons</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconDeviceTablet/> Mockups</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconPencil/> Illustrations</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconWorld/> Landing pages</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconDeviceTablet/> Mobile apps</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconPointer/> Web apps</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconDeviceDesktop/> Desktop apps</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconChartDonut2/> Dashboards</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconServer/> Custom backend</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconBrandFirebase/> Firebase</div>
				<div class="px-1 flex gap-4 items-center text-lg"><IconBrandSupabase/> Supabase</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<div class="h-32"></div>
	<section class="container mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
			<nav class="text-2xl w-full max-w-sm">
				<a class="flex items-center gap-4 text-black"><IconArrowDownRight size={28}/> Pricing</a>
				<div class="h-2"></div>
				<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">* You can change, pause or cancel your subscription anytime</p>
			</nav>
			<div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
				<div class="p-6 flex flex-col gap-4 border-[1px] rounded-2xl">
					<div class="flex items-center text-xl gap-4">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-black">Unlimited</h3>
						<span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-[18px] px-3 py-1 rounded-lg">$749 per week</span>
					</div>
					<p class="text-lg">Full development service to get your vision materialized with unlimited incremental changes</p>	
					<div class="flex justify-between">
						<span class="py-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-md text-black"><IconRefresh size={18}/> Cancel anytime</span>
						<a href="mailto: marcus.felix@gmail.com" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-2 text-lg bg-gray-200">Let's talk <IconArrowRight size={20}/></a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<div class="h-32"></div>
	<section class="container mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
			<nav class="text-2xl w-full max-w-sm">
				<span class="flex items-center gap-4 text-black"><IconArrowDownRight size={28}/> Frequent questions</span>
			</nav>
			<div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-6">
				<details>
					<summary class="flex items-center gap-4 list-none text-2xl text-black cursor-pointer">
						<span class="w-7 h-7 bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">1</span>
						Is there a request limit?
					</summary>
					<div class="py-4 text-lg pl-11">
						<p>Absolutely not! You can send as many requests you want, so they will be processed one at a time.</p>
					</div>
				</details>
				<hr/>
				<details>
					<summary class="flex items-center gap-4 list-none text-2xl text-black cursor-pointer">
						<span class="w-7 h-7 bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">2</span>
						How fast will my requests will be delivered?
					</summary>
					<div class="py-4 text-lg pl-11">
						<p>For simple designs or small code changes, you will receive a draft within 3 days max. More complex tasks will be splited in smaller ones so we can keep fast feedback loop times.</p>
					</div>
				</details>
				<hr/>
				<details>
					<summary class="flex items-center gap-4 list-none text-2xl text-black cursor-pointer">
						<span class="w-7 h-7 bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">3</span>
						What if i don't have more requests?
					</summary>
					<div class="py-4 text-lg pl-11">
						<p>You can simply pause your weekly subscription until you have more work to be done.</p>
					</div>
				</details>
				<hr/>
				<details>
					<summary class="flex items-center gap-4 list-none text-2xl text-black cursor-pointer">
						<span class="w-7 h-7 bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">4</span>
						What if i don't like the results?
					</summary>
					<div class="py-4 text-lg pl-11">
						<p>Don't worry, we'll continue with the feedback loop until you are 100% satisfied.</p>
					</div>
				</details>
				<hr/>
				<details>
					<summary class="flex items-center gap-4 list-none text-2xl text-black cursor-pointer">
						<span class="w-7 h-7 bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">5</span>
						Where can i submit my requests?
					</summary>
					<div class="py-4 text-lg pl-11">
						<p>You will have a private Slack channel where you can send requests and comunicate with our team. You can <a href="/start" class="text-blue-700">create your workspace</a> right now for free. Fell free to invite team mates to participate.</p>
					</div>
				</details>
				<hr/>
				<details>
					<summary class="flex items-center gap-4 list-none text-2xl text-black cursor-pointer">
						<span class="w-7 h-7 bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">6</span>
						Why weekly subscriptions?
					</summary>
					<div class="py-4 text-lg pl-11">
						<p>A week is the perfect time frame to plan, execute and test a complete feature. Keep delivering code is important to maintain your product evolving while serving users at the same time. With all that in mind, we offer weekly subscriptions as a complete unit of compreensive work to reduce risks and delivery value to our customers one week at time.</p>
					</div>
				</details>
				<hr/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Website>